==Japanese==
===Etymology===
[[連]] ([[れん]], ''ren''), "continuous" or "sequential" + [[濁]] ([[だく]], ''daku''), "voicing"

===Noun===
{{janoun|れんだく|rendaku}}

#  {{linguistics}} a morphological change of a non-initial syllable of many Japanese words from an [[unvoiced]] sound to a [[voiced]] one (more precisely, a change to the sound of corresponding kana with a [[濁点]])